curam.util.rules

Class TagResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.rules.TagResult

  • public class TagResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains either information used to determine the value of RulesObjectiveResultor non-financial information such as recommendation for other products or assessments associated with the achieved RulesObjectiveResult. A list of TagResult objects is provided by RulesResult.getTagResultList().

    Tags are defined at design time using the Rules Editor.
